# TRACKED EXCEPTIONS (force-include with git add -f)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The following are tracked via `git add -f`:
#   - requirements.txt
#   - Horne_et_al._2023_MB_BSMT_FSP_V1.shp (fault shapefile, 474 KB)
#   - tmle_shift_365d_v2_full.csv (production TMLE shift results)
#   - tmle_dose_response_365d_v2_full.csv (production TMLE dose-response)
#   - tmle_mediation_365d_20260412_203226.csv (production mediation)
#   - tmle_r_crossvalidation_7km_20260411.csv (R tlverse validation)
#   - positivity_diagnostics.csv (positivity report)
#   - positivity_shift.csv (shift H-statistic report)
#   - formation_sensitivity.csv (depth-proxy robustness)
#   - model_improvements_summary.csv (4-improvement comparison)
#   - evalue_sensitivity.csv (unmeasured confounding bounds)
#   - causal_well_day_simple.csv (OLS baseline results)
#   - causal_event_level_simple.csv (OLS event-level results)
